                                                                                                                            |   | allowSharedTabs                                    | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the account allows users to share custom tabs (fields). &lt;br&gt;   This setting is only shown when getting account settings. It cannot be modified.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |   | allowSignDocumentFromHomePage                      | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the Sign a Document Now button is available on the Home tab.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |   | allowSignatureStamps                               | Boolean | Reserved                                                    | Reserved for DocuSign.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     