                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |   | tabLockingEnabled                                  | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the locked option is available for tabs with that property.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |   | tabTextFormattingEnabled                           | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the formatting options (font type, font size, font color, bold, italic, and underline) are available for tabs with those properties.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |   | universalSignatureOptIn                            | Boolean | Reserved                                                    | Reserved for DocuSign.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           