elected in AccountSigningSettings| When **true**, the content of notification emails is determined at the account level.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   | useConsumerDisclosure                              | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the account  can use supplemental documents.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  